<lb n="0322a02" ed="A"/><list><item xml:id="itemA112p0322a0201">八十三部，一百七十卷，
<lb n="0322a03" ed="A"/><note n="0322a0301" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【金藏】</note><app n="0322a0301"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">已</lem><rdg wit="【金藏】">巳</rdg></app>編入前錄。</item></list></item></list></item></list></item>
<lb n="0322a04" ed="A"/><item xml:id="itemA112p0322a0401"><note n="0322a0401" resp="CBETA" type="add">新譯【CB】，［－］【金藏】</note><app n="0322a0401"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">新譯</lem><rdg wit="【金藏】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><list><item xml:id="itemA112p0322a0403"><note n="0322a0402" resp="CBETA" type="add">真宗朝【CB】，［－］【金藏】</note><app n="0322a0402"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">真宗朝</lem><rdg wit="【金藏】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><list><item xml:id="itemA112p0322a0406"><note n="0322a0403" resp="CBETA" type="add">大小乘經律論集【CB】，［－］【金藏】</note><app n="0322a0403"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">大小乘經、律、論集</lem><rdg wit="【金藏】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，一十二部，七十六卷，未
<lb n="0322a05" ed="A"/>編入錄。</item></list></item>
